title: S13 Ep62: Imaginary Friends or Intruders of the Supernatural

description:
Today BEYOND the DARKNESS wants to know, Imaginary Friends or Intruders of the Supernatural with guest Kylie Holmes.

What are Imaginary Friends? Kylie discusses some theories and Dave has a strange supernatural encounter in front of his eyes during the interview PLUS a Brand New THEATER of the MIND!

Get Kylie Holmes book here: www.Amazon.com/shop/darknessradio

Visit Kylie here: www.touchedbyanangel.me.uk
